snippet.title: Boomerang X - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Harness the power of a mystical boomerang to fling yourself through the air. Slice, fly, and blast through arenas swarming with evil creatures. Stay agile or meet your doom. 

Boomerang X is available now for Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/boomerang-x-switch/
